    "This consideration encompassed aspects such as diversity, context, and semantics.",
    "Additionally, in Sabty et al. (2021), data augmentation (DA) was employed to augment the limited amount of labeled data available for named entity recognition (NER).",
    "Various automatic augmentation techniques, such as back-translation, modified EDA, and word embedding substitution, were introduced to expand the training data and enhance the performance of Arabic NER.",
    "The study's findings demonstrated that the performance of NER can be improved through the application of combinations of different DA techniques.",
    "Automatically predicting misleading information in Arabic social media is both a technological and socio-cultural imperative."
